name: Cowboys & Indians SCRT 5-panel
description: Our limited edition premium black canvas 5 panel camp cap with buckle closure. Labelled at the front, back and inside. Collaboration with Denton Watts, illustrator and print-maker from Austin Texas. Working simple yet bold designs into lino-cuts. To see more of Denton's work click here.

name: Centurion - White
description: SCRT crossed swords left chest print and oversized centurion helmet backprint screen printed by hand onto our premium cotton white t-shirt. A collaboration with Iain Macarthur. Born in Swindon, England, Iain loved art from an early age. His work can be described as surreal and unique in its own way. Using mostly pencil, watercolours and pigment pens. More of his work can be found here. Please wash inside out at 30°C. All our tees, vests and sweatshirts are unisex.

name: Baboon - White
description: Oversized Baboon chest print screen printed by hand onto our premium cotton white t-shirt. A collaboration with Matty D'Arienzo. From Melbourne, now of London, Matty works out of INTO YOU TATTOO. Check out more of Matty's work here. Please wash inside out at 30°C. All our tees, vests and sweatshirts are unisex.
